INSERT INTO `accordion_items` (`id`, `service_id`, `title`, `content`) VALUES
(27, 91, 'How often should I get my AC ducts cleaned?', 'We recommend professional AC duct cleaning in JLT & Jumeirah every 6 to 12 months, depending on your usage and environmental factors.'),
(28, 91, 'What are the signs that my AC ducts need cleaning?', 'Common signs include dust accumulation around vents, musty odors, increased allergies, reduced airflow, and higher energy bills'),
(29, 91, 'Is AC duct cleaning safe for my family and pets?', 'Yes! Neat And Healthy Cleaning uses eco-friendly and non-toxic cleaning products, ensuring a safe environment for your loved ones.'),
(30, 91, 'Will AC duct cleaning help reduce my electricity bills?', 'Yes! Clean ducts improve airflow efficiency, reducing the workload on your AC unit and lowering energy consumption.'),
(31, 91, 'Do you provide AC duct cleaning for commercial properties?', 'Yes! We offer AC duct cleaning services in JLT & Jumeirah for both residential and commercial properties, including offices, restaurants, and retail spaces.'),
(32, 1, 'What is villa deep cleaning?', 'This is an in-depth cleaning service that goes beyond regular cleaning. It covers every corner of your home, including hard-to-reach areas like air vents, carpets, upholstery, and behind furniture. This service removes hidden dirt, dust, and bacteria to create a healthier living environment.'),
(33, 1, 'How often should I get villa deep cleaning?', 'We recommend scheduling at least once or twice a year. However, if you have pets, children, or suffer from allergies, you may need deep cleaning more frequently.'),
(34, 1, 'Do you provide cleaning for specific rooms in my villa?', 'Yes! We offer customized cleaning services. Whether it’s your kitchen, bathroom, bedrooms, or living areas, we focus on the areas that need the most attention. You can choose the rooms you\'d like cleaned in-depth.'),
(35, 1, 'Are your cleaning products safe for my family and pets?', 'Absolutely! At Neat & Healthy Cleaning, we use eco-friendly and non-toxic products that are safe for both your family and pets. We aim to provide a clean, safe home environment without compromising health.'),
(36, 1, 'How long does villa deep cleaning take?', 'The time required depends on the size of your villa and the extent of cleaning needed. On average, it takes 4 to 8 hours. We’ll give you an estimated timeframe before we begin.'),
(37, 1, 'Do I need to be home during the cleaning?', 'It’s not necessary, but we suggest being present for the first few minutes to discuss any specific cleaning needs or concerns. After that, you can leave your villa in our trusted hands.\n'),
(38, 1, 'Can you remove stains from carpets and upholstery?', 'Yes! We specialize in removing stubborn stains from carpets and upholstery. Our advanced techniques ensure your furniture and carpets are thoroughly cleaned and refreshed.'),
(39, 1, 'Are you a local cleaning company?', 'Yes, Neat & Healthy Cleaning is based in Dubai, and we specialise in deep cleaning and other professional cleaning services in the area. We’re proud to serve residents and businesses with reliable, high-quality solutions.'),
(40, 1, 'What sets Neat & Healthy Cleaning apart from other deep cleaning companies near me?', 'What makes us stand out is our commitment to customer satisfaction, highly trained staff, eco-friendly products, and meticulous attention to detail. We ensure your villa is thoroughly cleaned, sanitised, and refreshed every time.'),
(41, 1, 'How can I book a villa deep cleaning service?', 'Booking a villa deep cleaning service is easy! Just call us at [Your Contact Number], message us on WhatsApp, or fill out the booking form on our website. We’ll get in touch to schedule a time that works best for you.'),
(42, 2, 'What does your move-in/move-out cleaning service include?', 'Our service covers a full deep clean of the entire property. This includes dusting, vacuuming, mopping, and sanitising all rooms. We focus especially on kitchens and bathrooms, removing grease, soap scum, and any leftover residues to ensure a fresh and hygienic environment.'),
(43, 2, 'How much does move-out cleaning cost in Dubai?', 'The cost depends on the size of the property, its condition, and the cleaning services you need. We offer transparent pricing and provide a free, no-obligation quote tailored to your requirements.'),
(44, 2, 'Do I need to provide cleaning supplies or equipment?', ' No, we bring everything we need! Our team arrives with eco-friendly cleaning products and all the necessary equipment to get your space spotless.\n'),
(45, 2, 'How long does the move-in/move-out cleaning take?', 'The cleaning time varies depending on the property size and its condition. On average, it can take a few hours to a full day. We can provide a more accurate estimate when you request a quote.\n'),
(46, 2, 'Is your cleaning service eco-friendly?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly cleaning products that are safe for the environment, your family, and pets. You can relax knowing your space is clean and free from harmful chemicals.'),
(47, 2, 'Do I need to be present during the cleaning?', 'You don’t need to be there during the cleaning, but we recommend being available to show our team around beforehand and answer any questions. If you can\'t be there, we can arrange access instructions for you.'),
(48, 2, 'Can you clean my office or commercial space as well?', 'Of course! We also offer deep cleaning services for offices and commercial properties. Whether you need a one-time clean or regular maintenance, we can handle your business\'s cleaning needs.'),
(49, 2, 'How can I book a move-in/move-out cleaning service?', 'You can easily book by calling us at [Your Contact Number] or filling out our online booking form on our website. We’re here to help with all your cleaning needs!\n'),
(50, 4, 'What’s Included in a Floor Deep Cleaning Service?', 'A thorough floor deep cleaning includes:\n\n-Complete cleaning and sanitisation of all floor types.\n-Removal of embedded dirt, stains, and grime.\n-Use of appropriate cleaning agents tailored to each floor type.\n-Polishing and restoration to bring back the floor\'s shine.\n-This ensures your floors look great and are free from harmful bacteria and allergens.\n'),
(51, 4, 'How Often Should Floors Be Professionally Deep Cleaned?', 'How often you should get a professional deep clean depends on factors like foot traffic, floor type, and environmental conditions. Here’s a general guide:\n\n-Residential Spaces: Every 6 to 12 months.\n-Commercial Spaces: Every 3 to 6 months due to higher foot traffic.\n\nRegular cleaning helps maintain your floor\'s condition and extends its lifespan.\n'),
(52, 4, 'Are the Cleaning Products Used Safe for Children and Pets?', 'Yes! Trusted cleaning services use eco-friendly and non-toxic cleaning products. These are safe for children and pets and clean floors effectively without leaving harmful residues.'),
(53, 4, 'Can Deep Cleaning Remove Tough Stains and Odours from Floors?', 'Absolutely! Professional deep cleaning tackles:\n\n-Stubborn stains from spills and foot traffic.\n-Unpleasant odours from mold, mildew, or pet accidents.\n\nSpecialized equipment and cleaning agents reach deep into the flooring to eliminate these issues, leaving your floors fresh and clean.\n'),
(54, 4, 'How Long Does the Floor Deep Cleaning Process Take?', 'The cleaning time depends on:\n\n-Area size.\n-Floor type and condition.\n\nOn average:\n\n-Residential Areas: 2 to 4 hours.\n-Commercial Spaces: 4 to 8 hours or more, depending on the scope.\n'),
(55, 5, 'What does office deep cleaning include?', 'It covers a complete clean of floors, surfaces, restrooms, and high-touch areas. We use specialised equipment, like floor scrubbers and industrial cleaners, to ensure your floors are spotless. We also offer wood floor cleaning, move-in and move-out cleaning, and sanitisation of shared spaces to maintain a healthy work environment.'),
(56, 5, 'How often should I schedule deep cleaning for my office?', 'We recommend scheduling a deep clean every 3 to 6 months, depending on your office size and foot traffic. Regular maintenance cleaning can also help keep your office clean between deep cleans.'),
(57, 5, 'Do you clean hardwood floors in office spaces?', 'Yes, we specialise in hardwood floor cleaning. Our team uses high-quality wood floor cleaners to maintain the beauty and durability of your wooden floors while effectively removing dirt and stains.\n'),
(58, 5, ' How long does an office deep cleaning service take?', 'The time required depends on the size of your office and the specific services you need. On average, it can take anywhere from 3 to 8 hours. We’ll give you a more precise estimate after discussing your requirements.'),
(59, 5, 'Can I schedule office deep cleaning during office hours?', 'Yes, we can clean during office hours. However, to minimise disruption, many of our clients prefer deep cleaning after hours or on weekends. Let us know what works best for you, and we’ll adjust accordingly.\n'),
(60, 5, ' Do you offer cleaning services for other commercial spaces?', 'Yes, we offer a variety of commercial cleaning services, including carpet cleaning, window cleaning, post-construction cleaning, and janitorial services. We can tailor our services to meet the needs of any commercial space.\n'),
(61, 5, 'How much does office deep cleaning cost?', 'The cost depends on the size of your office, the services required, and how often cleaning is needed. We offer competitive pricing and will provide a custom quote after assessing your needs.'),
(62, 5, 'Is your cleaning service eco-friendly?', 'Yes, we use eco-friendly cleaning products whenever possible to ensure the safety of your employees and the environment. Our methods are effective yet gentle, offering a healthier alternative to harsh chemicals.'),
(63, 5, 'Will you bring your cleaning supplies?', 'Yes, we bring all the necessary cleaning supplies and equipment, including industrial floor cleaners, floor scrubbers, and wood floor cleaners. You don’t need to worry about a thing – just sit back and relax while we handle the cleaning.'),
(64, 5, 'How do I book office deep cleaning services?', 'Booking is easy! Simply contact us via our website or reach out directly for a free consultation. We’ll discuss your needs, create a customized plan, and schedule your cleaning at a time that suits you best.\n'),
(65, 6, 'How often should I have my sofa shampooed?', 'It’s recommended to have your sofa professionally shampooed every 6 to 12 months, depending on usage and exposure to dirt, pets, or allergens. If you notice stains or unpleasant odours before then, it’s a good idea to book a cleaning sooner.'),
(66, 6, 'Is sofa shampoo cleaning safe for all types of fabric?', 'Yes! Our team assesses your sofa\'s fabric type before applying the best cleaning methods. Whether it\'s cotton, linen, leather, or synthetic, we ensure a safe and effective clean.\n'),
(67, 6, 'How long does the sofa shampoo cleaning process take?', 'The cleaning process usually takes 1 to 2 hours, depending on the size and condition of your sofa. After cleaning, the sofa will need a few hours to dry completely.'),
(68, 6, 'Will all stains be removed during the cleaning?', 'While we aim to remove all stains, some older or deep-set stains may be harder to eliminate. We use the best techniques available, but results depend on how severe the stain is.'),
(69, 6, 'How long does it take for the sofa to dry after cleaning?', 'Drying usually takes around 4 to 6 hours, depending on the material, humidity, and cleaning method used. For faster drying, place the sofa in a well-ventilated area.'),
(70, 6, 'Are the cleaning products safe for children and pets?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly and non-toxic cleaning solutions, so your sofa is safe for both children and pets. You can feel confident that our methods are effective and safe.'),
(71, 6, 'Can you remove pet hair from my sofa?', 'Yes! We offer specialised cleaning to remove pet hair, dander, and other debris, leaving your sofa cleaner and your home healthier.'),
(72, 6, 'Do you offer cleaning for other furniture and upholstery?', 'Absolutely! Besides sofa cleaning, we also offer chair upholstery cleaning, mattress cleaning, and carpet cleaning. We can refresh all types of upholstered furniture in your home!\n'),
(73, 7, 'What is included in your kitchen deep cleaning service?', 'It covers cleaning and sanitising all surfaces, degreasing appliances, scrubbing floors, cleaning ovens and exhaust fans, disinfecting high-touch areas, and removing grease and grime from walls and ceilings. We pay attention to every detail to ensure your kitchen is thoroughly clean.'),
(74, 7, 'How often should I schedule a kitchen deep cleaning?', 'We recommend scheduling a deep clean every 1-3 months, depending on how much the kitchen is used. High-traffic kitchens, such as those in restaurants or commercial spaces, may need cleaning more frequently to maintain hygiene standards.\n'),
(75, 7, 'Is your kitchen deep cleaning service safe for food preparation areas?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are completely safe for food preparation areas. Our cleaning methods ensure that your kitchen remains hygienic and safe for cooking.\n'),
(76, 7, 'Do you offer deep cleaning for commercial and restaurant kitchens?', 'Yes! We specialise in commercial kitchen cleaning and restaurant kitchen cleaning services. Our team is equipped to handle kitchens of all sizes, ensuring they meet food safety and hygiene regulations.'),
(77, 7, 'How long does a kitchen deep cleaning take?', 'The time depends on the kitchen size and cleaning requirements. Typically, it takes between 3 to 8 hours. We’ll give you an estimate based on your specific needs.'),
(78, 7, 'Can I use my kitchen immediately after the cleaning?', 'Yes, your kitchen will be ready for use as soon as the cleaning is complete. We ensure the space is thoroughly clean and safe for food preparation.'),
(79, 7, 'Are your cleaning products environmentally friendly?', 'Absolutely! We use eco-friendly cleaning solutions that are both effective and safe for the environment. Our products are free from harsh chemicals, making them safe for your kitchen and the planet.\n'),
(80, 7, 'How can I book a kitchen deep cleaning service?', 'Booking is easy! Simply call us directly or fill out our online contact form. We’ll get back to you promptly to schedule your cleaning at a time that suits you.'),
(81, 9, 'What is included in your apartment deep cleaning service?', 'Our apartment cleaning services cover all areas: dusting, vacuuming, mopping, sanitizing bathrooms, cleaning kitchen surfaces, and deep cleaning carpets, upholstery, and appliances. We also target hard-to-reach spots that regular cleaning often misses.'),
(82, 9, 'How often should I book a deep cleaning service for my apartment?', 'For the best results, we recommend booking a deep clean every 3 to 6 months, depending on your lifestyle and how often you use your apartment. If you have pets or suffer from allergies, more frequent cleanings may be necessary.\n'),
(83, 9, 'Are your cleaning products eco-friendly?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly, non-toxic products that are safe for your family, pets, and the environment. We aim to create a cleaner, healthier home without compromising on quality.\n'),
(84, 9, 'How long does a deep cleaning service take?', 'The time required depends on the size of your apartment and the level of cleaning needed. Typically, it takes between 3 to 5 hours to thoroughly deep clean an apartment.'),
(85, 9, 'Do I need to be home during the cleaning?', 'You don’t have to be home. Our professional team can work while you\'re out, ensuring your apartment is spotless by the time you return.\n'),
(86, 9, 'Can I book a deep cleaning service on short notice?', 'Yes! We offer flexible scheduling and can accommodate last-minute bookings, depending on availability. For guaranteed timeslots, we recommend booking in advance.\n'),
(87, 9, 'How much does apartment deep cleaning cost?', 'The cost of apartment cleaning services varies depending on the size of your apartment and the services required. Contact us for a free, personalized quote.'),
(88, 9, 'Do you offer any discounts for repeat services?', 'Yes, we offer special discounts for regular customers. Contact us to learn more about our loyalty programs and promotions.'),
(89, 10, 'What does balcony cleaning include?', 'It covers a full wash of floors, railings, and walls, along with balcony window cleaning and glass cleaning. We remove dirt, grime, and stains to ensure your outdoor space is spotless and safe.'),
(90, 10, 'How often should I clean my balcony?', 'In Dubai’s dusty environment, we recommend cleaning your apartment balcony every 3-4 months. If your balcony is exposed to sandstorms or heavy weather, more frequent cleaning may be necessary to keep it looking its best.'),
(91, 10, 'Why should I hire professionals for balcony cleaning?', 'Hiring professionals guarantees a deep, thorough clean with the right tools and techniques. We can safely clean hard-to-reach areas like windows and high railings, saving you time and effort while achieving superior results.'),
(92, 10, 'Can cleaning improve my property\'s value?', 'Yes! A clean, well-maintained balcony boosts your home’s overall aesthetic and curb appeal. It’s an easy yet effective way to maintain your property’s value and create a welcoming outdoor space.'),
(93, 10, 'Do you use eco-friendly products for cleaning?', 'Absolutely! We prioritize eco-friendly cleaning solutions that are safe for both you and the environment. Our products effectively remove dirt without damaging surfaces or harming the surrounding area.\n'),
(94, 10, 'How long does it take to clean a balcony?', 'The time required for balcony deep cleaning depends on the size and condition of the space. Typically, it takes 1-2 hours. We’ll provide a specific estimate based on your balcony’s needs.'),
(95, 10, 'Is balcony glass cleaning included in your services?', 'Yes! Balcony glass cleaning is part of our complete cleaning package. We ensure your windows and glass surfaces are sparkling clean, offering you a clear, unobstructed view from your balcony.'),
(96, 11, 'How often should I schedule a garage deep cleaning?', 'We recommend scheduling a garage deep cleaning at least once a year to maintain cleanliness and prevent clutter buildup. If your garage gets a lot of use, more frequent cleanings might be necessary.'),
(97, 11, 'What types of stains can you remove from my garage floor?', 'Our team is equipped to remove various stains, including oil, grease, rust, and dirt. We use specialized cleaning agents that break down tough stains without damaging your floor.'),
(99, 11, 'Do you provide garage decluttering services?', 'Yes! Along with deep cleaning, we offer garage decluttering services to help you sort through and remove unwanted items, creating a more organized and functional space.'),
(100, 11, ' Are your cleaning products safe for the environment?', 'Absolutely! We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products to ensure a safe and healthy environment for your family and pets.'),
(101, 11, 'How long does the garage cleaning process take?', 'The time required for cleaning depends on the size and condition of your garage. On average, it takes between 3 to 6 hours to complete the process.'),
(102, 11, 'Can you help with organizing my garage after cleaning?', ' Yes, our service includes organizing your garage items and suggesting the best storage solutions to maximize space and improve accessibility.\n'),
(103, 11, 'Do you offer garage cleaning for all types of garages?', 'Yes, we clean all types of garages, whether residential or commercial, including those with extensive clutter or heavy-duty cleaning needs.'),
(104, 12, 'What is steam deep cleaning?', 'Steam deep cleaning uses high-pressure steam to clean and sanitize surfaces like carpets, upholstery, and curtains. It effectively removes dirt, stains, allergens, and bacteria—without the need for harsh chemicals.'),
(105, 12, 'Is steam cleaning safe for my upholstery and curtains?', 'Yes, steam cleaning is safe for most upholstery and curtains. The steam penetrates deep into the fabric to lift dirt and stains while being gentle on delicate materials.'),
(106, 12, 'How long does it take for steam-cleaned carpets to dry?', 'Steam-cleaned carpets usually dry within 2-4 hours, depending on the humidity and airflow in the room.'),
(107, 12, 'Can steam cleaning remove pet odors?', 'Absolutely! Steam cleaning is excellent at neutralizing pet odors and stains, leaving your carpets and upholstery smelling fresh.'),
(108, 12, 'Is steam cleaning better than traditional carpet cleaning?', 'Yes, steam cleaning often works better because it reaches deeper into fibers, removes bacteria and allergens, and leaves no residue. It’s a more thorough and eco-friendly option compared to traditional methods.'),
(109, 12, 'Is steam cleaning safe for my family and pets?', 'Yes, steam cleaning is completely safe and chemical-free, making it ideal for homes with children and pets. It sanitizes surfaces without leaving harmful chemicals or residues.'),
(110, 12, 'How often should I get my carpets and upholstery steam cleaned?', ' For the best results, it\'s recommended to steam clean your carpets and upholstery every 6-12 months. If you have pets or suffer from allergies, you may want to do it more often.'),
(111, 13, 'How much does it cost to deep clean an oven or BBQ grill?', 'The cost varies depending on the size and condition of the appliance. Contact us for a free, personalized quote based on your specific needs.\n'),
(112, 13, 'How often should I deep clean my oven or BBQ grill?', 'For the best performance, we suggest deep cleaning your oven every 3-6 months. For your BBQ grill, clean it after each grilling season or every 3-6 months, depending on how often you use it.\n'),
(113, 13, 'What does your oven and BBQ cleaning service include?', 'Our service involves a detailed cleaning of your oven or BBQ grill, removing grease, grime, and food residue. We also clean those hard-to-reach areas, leaving your appliances spotless and fully functional.\n'),
(114, 13, 'Are the cleaning products you use safe for my family and pets?', 'Absolutely! We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are safe for your family, pets, and the environment, ensuring a healthy cooking space.'),
(115, 13, 'Can I clean my BBQ grill myself?', 'You can, but professional cleaning guarantees a deeper, more thorough result. We reach areas that are often missed with DIY methods, giving you a cleaner and more efficient BBQ grill.'),
(116, 13, 'How long does the cleaning process take?', 'The cleaning process usually takes 1-2 hours for an oven and 1-3 hours for a BBQ grill, depending on the size and condition of the appliance.\n'),
(117, 13, 'Do you offer regular cleaning services?', 'Yes! We offer regular cleaning services to keep your oven and BBQ grill in top condition. Get in touch with us for a tailored cleaning schedule that fits your needs.'),
(118, 14, 'How often should I schedule deep cleaning for my restaurant?', 'It’s recommended to schedule restaurant deep cleaning services at least once a month, depending on the size and type of your restaurant. High-traffic restaurants may need more frequent cleaning to maintain the best hygiene.'),
(119, 14, 'What areas of my restaurant are covered in deep cleaning?  ', 'Our commercial kitchen deep cleaning services cover all essential areas, including kitchen equipment, hoods, exhaust systems, floors, restrooms, dining areas, and high-touch surfaces. We make sure every corner is thoroughly cleaned.'),
(120, 14, 'Are the cleaning products used safe for food preparation areas?', 'Yes, we use eco-friendly and food-safe cleaning agents. They effectively sanitize without leaving harmful residues, ensuring your kitchen and dining areas stay safe for food preparation and service.\n'),
(121, 14, 'Can I schedule deep cleaning during off-hours?', 'Absolutely! We offer flexible scheduling and can perform deep cleaning during off-peak hours or overnight to avoid disrupting your operations.'),
(122, 14, 'Do you offer steam cleaning for kitchen equipment?', 'Yes, we offer restaurant steam-cleaning services to deeply sanitize kitchen equipment, floors, and surfaces without harsh chemicals. Steam cleaning is safe and highly effective at removing grease and bacteria.'),
(123, 14, 'How can deep cleaning help me pass health inspections?', 'Regular deep cleaning ensures your restaurant meets and exceeds health and safety regulations. Our services help you avoid fines and pass health inspections with confidence by maintaining top-notch hygiene.'),
(124, 14, 'Can you help with pest prevention?', 'Yes, deep cleaning removes food residue and grease buildup, which are common attractants for pests. Our thorough cleaning reduces the risk of infestations and helps maintain a pest-free environment.'),
(125, 14, 'Do you provide a certificate of cleaning for health inspections?', 'Yes, we can provide certification after completing your deep cleaning service, which will help with documentation for health inspections and ensure compliance.\n'),
(127, 15, 'What is included in your nightclub cleaning service?', 'Our nightclub cleaning service covers deep cleaning of floors, furniture, surfaces, restrooms, and high-touch areas like bar counters and door handles. We also handle stain removal, trash disposal, and sanitization to ensure your venue stays spotless and hygienic.'),
(128, 15, 'How often should my club or bar be cleaned?', 'The frequency of cleaning depends on your club’s traffic and hours of operation. Typically, a deep clean should be done weekly, but high-traffic areas might need more frequent attention. We can create a customised schedule based on your specific needs.'),
(129, 15, 'Do you offer after-hours cleaning services?', 'Yes! We know your club needs to stay open for business, so we offer flexible after-hours cleaning to avoid disturbing your guests. Our team will clean during off-peak hours, ensuring your venue is ready for the next day.'),
(130, 15, 'Are your cleaning products safe for my venue?', 'Absolutely. We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are safe for both your staff and guests. Our products are tough on grime and bacteria but gentle on your furniture and floors.'),
(131, 15, 'How long does it take to clean a nightclub?', 'The time it takes depends on the size and condition of your venue. On average, a thorough deep clean takes a few hours, but we can provide an estimated time based on your club’s specific needs.'),
(132, 15, 'Can you clean during special events or parties?', 'Yes! We can arrange quick touch-up cleaning during events or parties to keep your venue looking pristine. We also offer post-event cleaning services to handle the clean-up after large gatherings.'),
(133, 15, 'How do I book your cleaning services?', 'Simply reach out to us through our contact page or give us a call. We’ll discuss your needs, set up a schedule, and arrange for our team to come in and clean your club.'),
(134, 15, 'Why is professional cleaning important for my nightclub?', 'A clean nightclub creates a more inviting and comfortable atmosphere for your guests, leading to better reviews and increased customer satisfaction. It also helps maintain hygiene, ensuring a safe environment for everyone. Regular professional cleaning extends the life of your furniture and flooring, keeping your venue looking its best.\n'),
(135, 40, 'What painting services do you offer?', 'We offer a wide range of services, including interior and exterior painting for apartments, villas, and commercial properties. Our services cover walls, ceilings, doors, trim, and more.\n'),
(136, 40, 'How much does house painting cost in Dubai?', 'The cost of house painting varies based on the size of your property:\nStudio apartment: AED 500 – 700\n\n\n1-bedroom apartment: AED 700 – 900\n\n\n3-bedroom apartment: AED 1,400 – 1,800\n\n\n2-bedroom villa: AED 1,800 – 2,300\n\n\n3-bedroom villa: AED 2,000 – 2,200\n\n\n4-bedroom villa: AED 3,000 – 3,500\n\n\nFor a more accurate estimate, we offer free consultations and detailed quotes.\n'),
(137, 40, 'How long does it take to paint a house?', 'The duration of a house painting project depends on the size of your home. For smaller apartments, the job can take one to two days, while larger villas may take three to four days. We always aim to finish projects on time with minimal disruption.'),
(138, 40, 'Do you provide eco-friendly paint options?', 'Yes, we offer low-VOC, eco-friendly paint options that are safe for your family and the environment. These paints are durable, long-lasting, and ideal for homes with children or pets.\n'),
(139, 40, 'Can I choose the color for my home?', 'Absolutely! Our expert painters can help you choose the perfect colour scheme for your home. We offer colour consultation services to ensure your choice complements your space and style.\n'),
(140, 40, 'Do you offer residential and commercial painting?', 'Yes, we cater to both residential and commercial painting projects. Whether you need painting for your home or office, our team has the expertise to deliver high-quality results every time.\n'),
(141, 40, 'How can I get a quote for painting my house?', 'Getting a quote is easy! Simply contact us to schedule a free site visit, and one of our expert painters will assess your space, discuss your requirements, and provide a detailed quote.\n'),
(142, 40, 'Do you clean up after the job is done?', 'Absolutely! We take pride in leaving your home spotless. Our team will clean up all painting materials and ensure your property looks as good as new once the job is complete.\n'),
(143, 80, 'How often should I repaint my home\'s exterior in Dubai?', 'Due to the extreme weather, it\'s recommended to repaint your home’s exterior every 5-7 years. The intense sun and sandstorms can cause the paint to fade, crack, or peel quickly, so regular touch-ups are necessary to keep your home looking great and protected.'),
(144, 80, 'What types of paint are best suited for Dubai\'s climate?', 'We use high-quality, weather-resistant paints designed to withstand intense heat and humidity. UV-resistant and moisture-resistant paints are ideal for protecting your home’s exterior from fading and damage.'),
(145, 80, 'How long does the exterior painting process take?', 'The time it takes to paint your home depends on its size and complexity. On average, the job takes between 3 to 7 days, including surface preparation and multiple coats of paint. We work efficiently to minimise disruption to your daily life.'),
(146, 80, 'Do you offer warranties on your painting services?', 'Yes, we offer a warranty on all our exterior painting services. Our premium paints and professional application ensure long-lasting results, but if any issues arise within the warranty period, we’ll address them promptly.'),
(147, 80, 'Can you assist with colour selection for my home’s exterior?', 'Definitely! Our expert team will help you choose the perfect colors to complement your home’s design and the surrounding environment. We’ll guide you in selecting a palette that enhances your property’s curb appeal.\n'),
(148, 84, 'How much does it cost to paint the interior of my home in Dubai?', 'The cost depends on factors like the size of your space, the condition of your walls, the type of paint you choose, and the level of detail required. At Neat and Healthy Cleaning, we offer custom quotes tailored to your needs. Contact us for a free, no-obligation estimate.'),
(149, 84, 'How long does it take to complete an interior painting project?', 'The timeline varies based on the size and complexity of the job. On average, painting a standard room takes one to two days, while larger spaces like villas may take several days. We\'ll provide a clear timeline during your consultation to keep you informed.'),
(150, 84, 'Do I need to prepare my home before the painters arrive?', 'It\'s helpful to remove valuable items and cover fragile furniture. Our team will handle the rest—preparing surfaces, protecting your belongings, and ensuring a clean environment. We aim to make the process easy and stress-free for you.'),
(151, 84, 'Can I choose my paint colours?', 'Absolutely! We offer a colour consultation to help you choose the perfect shades for your space. Our team will guide you through the selection process, considering your preferences, existing décor, and lighting conditions.'),
(152, 84, 'Are the paints you use safe for my family and pets?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly, low-VOC paints that are safe for both children and pets. Our paints provide a beautiful finish and contribute to better air quality in your home.'),
(153, 84, 'How can I find reliable interior painters near me?', 'At Neat and Healthy Cleaning, we’re proud to be one of the top painting companies near you. Our painters are skilled, experienced, and committed to delivering exceptional results. Simply reach out to us for a consultation, and we’ll bring the expertise to your doorstep!'),
(154, 84, 'Do you offer any guarantees on your painting services?', 'Yes! We offer a satisfaction guarantee. If you’re not happy with the results, we’ll work with you to resolve any issues. Your satisfaction is our top priority.'),
(155, 84, 'Can you help me with painting my office or commercial space?', 'Definitely! We also specialize in commercial interior painting, offering services for offices, retail spaces, and more. Whether it’s a fresh coat or a complete transformation, we provide professional, efficient painting services tailored to your business needs.'),
(156, 86, 'How much does it cost to paint a villa in Dubai?', 'The cost depends on the size of your villa and the type of paint used. For example, a 2-bedroom villa typically costs between AED 1,800 and 2,300, while a 4-bedroom villa may range from AED 3,000 to 3,500. We offer free site visits and personalised quotes.'),
(157, 86, 'How long does it take to paint a villa?', 'Most villa painting projects are completed within 2 to 5 days, depending on the size and scope of the work. We always stick to the agreed timelines to minimise disruption.\n\n\n'),
(158, 86, 'Do you use eco-friendly or low-odour paints?', 'Yes, we use high-quality, eco-friendly, low-VOC paints that are safe for families, children, and pets—ideal for interior and exterior use.\n'),
(159, 86, 'Can I stay in my villa while it’s being painted?', ' In most cases, yes. We work in sections and take extra care to minimise fumes and mess, making it safe and comfortable for you to stay home during the process.'),
(160, 86, 'Do you offer interior and exterior villa painting?', 'Absolutely! We specialise in both interior and exterior painting. Whether you want to refresh your living space or give your villa’s facade a makeover, we’ve got you covered.'),
(161, 86, 'Do you provide colour consultation services?', 'Yes, we do. Our experts help you choose the perfect colours that match your style, lighting, and villa design.'),
(162, 86, 'Is surface preparation included in the service?', 'Yes. We handle all prep work—cleaning, sanding, filling cracks, and priming surfaces—to ensure a smooth, long-lasting finish.\n'),
(163, 87, 'How much does apartment painting cost in Dubai?', 'The price varies based on the size of your apartment. Generally, it ranges from:\n\n\nStudio Apartment: AED 500 - AED 700\n\n\n1-Bedroom Apartment: AED 700 - AED 900\n\n\n3-Bedroom Apartment: AED 1400 - AED 1800\n For a more accurate quote, contact us for a free estimate.'),
(164, 87, 'How long does it take to paint an apartment?', 'The time needed depends on the size and the complexity of the project. A studio or 1-bedroom apartment typically takes 1-2 days, while a 3-bedroom apartment may take 2-3 days. Our team works efficiently to minimise disruption to your daily routine.'),
(165, 87, 'What should I expect when hiring apartment painters? ', 'When you hire our apartment painters, you can expect a smooth, professional process. Our team will:\n\n\nProvide a free consultation and estimate.\n\n\nPrepare your space by protecting furniture and floor.s\n\n\nUse high-quality paints and too.ls\n\n\nComplete the job quickly, with attention to diet.ail\n\n\nClean up and leave your apartment looking fresh and spotless.\n'),
(166, 87, 'Can apartment painters help with both the interior and exterior? ', 'Yes, our apartment painters are skilled in both interior and exterior painting. Whether you want to refresh your living room walls or give your apartment’s exterior a new coat, we’ve got you covered.'),
(167, 87, 'What type of paint is best for apartments?', 'The best type of paint for your apartment depends on the desired finish and the room’s usage. We recommend matte or satin finishes for a smooth, elegant look for interior walls. Semi-gloss or gloss paints are ideal for high-traffic areas like kitchens or bathrooms as they are more durable and easier to clean.'),
(168, 87, 'How do I choose the right apartment painters?', 'When choosing apartment painters, look for:\n\n\nExperience and reputation in the industry\n\n\nTransparent pricing with no hidden fees\n\n\nHigh-quality materials and tools\n\n\nPositive reviews and customer testimonials\n\n\nA professional approach to preparation, painting, and cleanup\n At Neat and Healthy Cleaning, we guarantee all these qualities for a top-notch painting experience.'),
(169, 87, 'Can I pick my colours for the painting?', 'Absolutely! We offer colour consultation services to help you choose the perfect shades that match your style and the ambience you want to create. Whether you have a specific colour in mind or need advice, we\'re here to guide you.\n'),
(170, 87, 'Does a warranty cover your painting services?', 'Yes, we offer a guarantee on our painting services. If you experience any issues with the paint job, we’ll address them promptly and make it right. Our goal is to ensure you’re delighted with the results.'),
(171, 88, 'How often should I repaint my building’s exterior in Dubai?', 'It’s recommended that your building’s exterior be repainted every 5 to 7 years, depending on factors like climate exposure, the condition of the current paint, and the material of your property. Regular maintenance can help prevent damage and keep your building looking fresh.\n'),
(172, 88, 'Can I choose any colour for my façade, or are there limitations?', 'You have plenty of colour options, but it’s essential to consider the building’s architecture, the surrounding environment, and the maintenance needs. We offer personalised consultations to help you choose a colour that fits your property and style.\n'),
(173, 88, 'What type of paint do you use for façade painting?', 'We use high-quality, weather-resistant paints designed explicitly for Dubai\'s harsh climate. Our paints are eco-friendly and low-VOC, making them safe for your property and the environment.\n'),
(174, 88, 'Will painting the façade protect my building from the elements?', 'Yes! A fresh coat of paint creates a protective barrier against the sun, rain, and humidity, helping preserve your building’s structure and prevent damage like cracking, peeling, and fading.'),
(175, 88, 'How long will it take to complete the façade painting?', 'The time it takes depends on the size of the building and the complexity of the project. On average, it takes a few days to a week. We aim to complete all projects efficiently without compromising on quality.'),
(176, 88, 'Do you offer colour consultation services?', 'We offer expert colour consultations to help you choose the best colour for your façade. Our team will consider your building’s design, location, and personal or brand preferences to recommend the right options.'),
(177, 88, ' Is exterior façade painting a one-time solution, or will I need to repaint often?', 'Exterior painting is a long-term solution, but depending on exposure to the elements, you may need to touch up or repaint every few years. Regular maintenance will help prolong the life of your paint and keep your building looking pristine.'),
(178, 88, 'Is the painting process disruptive?', 'We strive to minimise any disruption to your daily routine. Our team works efficiently, and we keep the surrounding areas clean and protected throughout the project.'),
(179, 88, 'Do you offer any warranties on your painting services?', 'Yes, we offer warranties on our artistry and the durability of our paints. This guarantees you a high-quality finish that lasts, giving you peace of mind.'),
(180, 88, 'How do I get started with a painting project?', 'Getting started is simple! Just contact us for a free consultation. Our team will assess your property, discuss your vision, and provide a detailed plan and quote for the project.'),
(181, 74, 'What types of paint do you use for wall painting services?', 'We use premium, eco-friendly, and non-toxic paints that are safe for you and your family. Our range includes a variety of colours, from classic whites to bold greens, blacks, and elegant golds, perfect for any style or space.'),
(182, 74, 'How do I choose the right colour for my room?', 'The right colour depends on the room’s purpose, lighting, and décor. If you need help, our team can help you choose the perfect palette that suits your space and style.\n'),
(183, 74, 'How long does the wall painting process take?', 'The time needed depends on the size and complexity of the project. On average, most rooms can be painted within a day or two. We will provide you with an accurate timeline before we begin.\n'),
(184, 74, 'Is the paint safe for my family and pets?', 'Yes, absolutely! We use low-VOC (volatile organic compounds) and non-toxic paints that are safe for children and pets, making your home healthier and eco-friendly.\n'),
(185, 74, 'How do I maintain the painted walls after the service?', 'Once the paint is dry, maintaining it is simple. Just wipe your walls with a damp cloth to keep them clean. Avoid using harsh chemicals or scrubbing too hard for long-lasting results.\n'),
(186, 74, 'Do I need to move furniture before the painting service?', 'We recommend clearing the area around the walls for a smoother job. Don’t worry; our team will protect your furniture and floors with covers and drop cloths.\n'),
(187, 74, 'Will the paint job last in Dubai’s hot climate?', 'Yes! Our high-quality paints are designed to withstand heat and sun. With proper application, your walls will stay vibrant and durable for years.\n'),
(188, 74, 'Can I get a custom colour for my walls?', 'Definitely! We offer custom colour options. If you have a specific shade, let us know, and we’ll match it perfectly.\n'),
(189, 75, 'How often should I repaint my office?', 'The frequency of repainting depends on foot traffic and the condition of your walls. Typically, offices should be repainted every 3 to 5 years to keep a fresh, professional appearance. High-traffic areas may need more frequent touch-ups.\n'),
(190, 75, 'What is the best colour for an office?', 'The best colour depends on the atmosphere you want to create. Blues and greens are calming and help with focus, while yellow and orange promote creativity and energy—neutral colours like grey or beige offer a sleek, professional look. We can guide you in choosing the ideal shade for your business.\n'),
(191, 75, 'How long will the painting take?', 'The time required depends on your office’s size and the project\'s complexity. Most office painting jobs are completed in 1 to 3 days. We work quickly to minimise disruption to your operations.'),
(192, 75, 'Do I need to move furniture before the painting starts?', 'We recommend moving smaller items, but our team can assist with covering and protecting larger furniture, equipment, and flooring to prevent any damage during the process.\n'),
(193, 75, 'Is it safe to paint an office while it’s in use?', 'Yes, we offer flexible scheduling to work around your office hours. Our team uses low-odour, eco-friendly paints, ensuring a healthy work environment for both employees and clients during the painting process.'),
(194, 75, 'Can you match specific colours or paint brands?', 'Absolutely! We can match any colour or paint brand you prefer. Just let us know your desired shade, and we’ll source the perfect match for your office.'),
(195, 75, 'What is the cost of office painting services in Dubai?', 'The cost varies depending on the size of the space, the type of paint, and the job\'s complexity. We provide free consultations and detailed, upfront quotes so you know what to expect.\n'),
(196, 75, 'How can I get started with your painting services?', 'Simply contact us for a free consultation. We’ll assess your office, discuss your vision, and provide a tailored quote. Our team will guide you every step of the way to ensure your office looks its best.\n'),
(197, 76, 'How long does the exterior parquet painting process take?', 'The process usually takes 2 to 4 days, depending on the size and condition of the area. This includes cleaning, sanding, painting, and drying time.\n'),
(198, 76, 'Will the new paint withstand Dubai\'s extreme weather?', 'Yes, we use top-quality, weather-resistant paints specifically designed for outdoor wooden surfaces. These paints provide durability and protection against Dubai\'s hot weather, humidity, and occasional rain.'),
(199, 76, 'How often should I repaint my exterior parquet flooring?', 'We recommend repainting every 2 to 3 years to keep your floors looking great and protect them from the elements.'),
(200, 76, 'Can you match the paint colour to my existing outdoor decor?', 'Of course! We offer various colours and finishes to complement your outdoor style. Our team will guide you through the selection process, ensuring a perfect match for your space.'),
(201, 76, ' Is the painting process safe for pets and children?', 'Yes, we use eco-friendly, low-VOC paints that are safe for pets and children once fully cured. We also ensure the area is well-ventilated during the process to reduce exposure, giving you peace of mind about the safety of the process.\n'),
(202, 76, 'Do you provide a warranty on your exterior parquet painting service?', 'Yes, we offer a warranty on our work, ensuring that the finish stays durable and any issues with the paint are quickly addressed.\n'),
(203, 76, 'Will painting my parquet flooring improve its longevity?', 'Absolutely! Exterior painting enhances the look and adds an extra layer of protection, greatly extending the life of your parquet flooring.'),
(204, 77, 'How often should I repaint my metal fence in Dubai?', 'You should repaint your metal fence every 3 to 5 years to protect it from rust and corrosion caused by Dubai’s extreme climate. Regular touch-ups will help keep it looking great and lasting longer.'),
(205, 77, 'Can Neat & Healthy Cleaning paint over existing rust?', 'We remove all rust using [specific method or tool] before applying fresh paint. This ensures a smooth, long-lasting finish and prevents further rust from forming.'),
(206, 77, 'What types of metal fences do you service?', 'We paint all metal fences, including wrought iron, steel, aluminium, and galvanised metal. Whether you need a small gate or a large boundary fence, we\'ve got you covered.'),
(207, 77, 'Are the paints used safe for surrounding plants and pets?', 'Are the paints used safe for surrounding plants and pets? Absolutely. We use eco-friendly, low-VOC paints that are safe for plants, pets, and children once fully cured, ensuring no harm to your environment.'),
(208, 77, 'How long does the metal fence painting process take?', 'The time needed depends on the size and condition of your fence. Most projects are completed within a few days with minimal disruption to your property.'),
(209, 77, 'Can I choose the colour and finish for my metal fence?', 'Absolutely! We offer various colours and finishes to suit your property’s style. Our team will guide you in choosing the perfect look for your fence.'),
(210, 77, 'Will the paint protect my fence from rust in the long term?', 'Our high-quality, weather-resistant paints are specifically formulated to protect against rust and corrosion, providing long-term durability and keeping your metal fence looking vibrant.'),
(211, 78, 'How often should I repaint my home’s exterior in Dubai?', 'It’s recommended to repaint your home’s exterior every 5-7 years, depending on exposure to the elements and the quality of the previous paint job. Due to Dubai\'s harsh weather, you may need more frequent touch-ups.'),
(212, 78, 'Can you help me choose the right paint colours for my home?', 'Yes! Our experts offer colour consultation to help you select the perfect shades that match your home’s style and the local environment. We ensure the colours complement your architecture and boost your home’s curb appeal.'),
(213, 78, 'Do you offer eco-friendly paint options?', 'Absolutely! We provide environmentally friendly, low-VOC paints that are safe for your family and the planet. These paints deliver a durable finish without harming the environment or your home’s health.'),
(214, 78, 'Will your paints withstand Dubai’s extreme weather conditions?', 'Yes! We use high-quality, weather-resistant paints specially formulated to resist intense heat, humidity, and sandstorms. Our paints resist fading, peeling, and cracking, offering long-lasting protection.'),
(215, 78, 'Can you paint wooden surfaces on my home’s exterior?', 'Yes, we specialise in wood exterior paint, offering protective coatings that enhance the natural beauty of wooden surfaces while shielding them from Dubai\'s harsh climate.'),
(216, 78, 'How long will the exterior painting process take?', 'The time it takes depends on the size of your home and the condition of the surfaces. Generally, most exterior painting projects are completed within a few days, causing minimal disruption to your daily routine.');
INSERT INTO `accordion_items` (`id`, `service_id`, `title`, `content`) VALUES
(217, 78, 'Are your painters licensed and insured?', 'Yes, all our painters are fully licensed and insured, ensuring professional, reliable, and safe service. We take every precaution to deliver high-quality work while maintaining a secure environment.\n'),
(218, 78, 'Do I need to prepare my home before painting?', 'We handle all the preparation work, including cleaning and surface repairs, so you don’t have to worry. Our team ensures your home is ready for a smooth, flawless paint application.'),
(219, 81, 'How often should I repaint my ceiling?', 'Ceilings should generally be repainted every 5-7 years. This depends on factors like room usage, moisture levels, and the condition of the current paint. Rooms with high humidity, such as kitchens and bathrooms, may need more frequent touch-ups.'),
(220, 81, 'Can you paint over old stains or water damage?', 'Yes! Our expert team can effectively cover stains and water damage. We’ll leave your ceiling looking smooth and flawless with proper preparation and top-quality paint.'),
(221, 81, 'Is ceiling painting a messy job?', 'Not at all! We take great care to protect your space, covering furniture and floors to prevent mess and ensuring the process is as clean and hassle-free as possible.'),
(222, 81, 'What types of paints do you use for ceiling painting?', 'We use high-quality, eco-friendly paints that are durable, low-VOC, and safe for your home or office. These paints provide long-lasting coverage while maintaining a healthier indoor environment.'),
(223, 81, 'How long does it take to paint a ceiling?', 'The time required depends on the size and condition of the ceiling. Typically, the job takes a few hours to a day. We’ll provide a more accurate estimate during your consultation.'),
(224, 81, 'Can you match specific colours or finishes for my ceiling?', 'Yes! Whether you prefer a matte, satin, or glossy finish, we can match the perfect colour and finish to suit your style and interior design.'),
(225, 81, 'Do I need to prepare my home before you arrive?', 'We handle all the preparation, including covering furniture and floors to protect them from paint splatters. We recommend removing any fragile items or décor that may be in the way.'),
(226, 81, 'Are your services available across all areas of Dubai?', 'Yes, we offer ceiling painting services all over Dubai, from Downtown to Jumeirah, Palm Jumeirah, Dubai Marina, and beyond. Wherever you are, we’ve got you covered!'),
(227, 82, 'What is antifungal wall painting?', 'Antifungal wall painting is a unique service for applying mould-resistant paint or coating to your walls. This paint contains antimicrobial agents that help stop mould, mildew, and fungi from growing, keeping your space clean and healthy.'),
(228, 82, 'How does antifungal paint prevent mould?', 'Antifungal paint has active ingredients that stop the growth of mould and mildew. These ingredients prevent moisture from being absorbed into the walls, creating an environment where fungi cannot survive.'),
(229, 82, 'Is antifungal paint safe for indoor use?', 'Yes, high-quality antifungal paints are safe for indoor use. They are nontoxic and release very few fumes, making them suitable for homes and businesses.'),
(230, 82, 'How long does antifungal paint last?', 'Antifungal paint can last several years, providing long-lasting protection against mould and mildew when appropriately applied and well-maintained. The paint\'s durability depends on humidity and wall conditions, but it is designed to give lasting protection.'),
(231, 82, 'Can antifungal paint be applied over existing mould?', 'While antifungal paint prevents future mould growth, it is best to clean and treat any existing mould before applying the paint. This ensures the paint sticks properly and works effectively.'),
(232, 82, 'How soon can I use the painted area after application?', 'After applying antifungal paint, it typically dries within 24 hours. However, wait 48 hours before placing heavy furniture or decorations on the walls for the best results, to allow the paint to cure fully.'),
(233, 82, 'Do I need to reapply antifungal paint regularly?', 'Antifungal paint offers long-term protection, but it\'s a good idea to check the paint every few years. If you notice wear or fungal growth, it may be time to apply a new coat to keep your walls protected.'),
(234, 83, 'How long does the parquet painting process take?', 'The time required depends on the size of the area and the condition of your floors. Generally, it takes between 1 and 3 days, including drying time.'),
(235, 83, 'Will the paint peel or fade over time?', 'No! We use high-quality, durable paints and finishes designed to handle wear and tear. Our coatings are made to last, even in Dubai’s climate.'),
(236, 83, 'Is the paint safe for my family and pets?', 'Absolutely! We use low-VOC, non-toxic paints that are safe for your family and pets, so you can relax while your floors are transformed.'),
(237, 83, 'Can you match the paint colour to my existing decor?', 'Yes! We offer various colours and finishes to suit your home’s style perfectly. Our team will help you choose the best option for your space.'),
(238, 83, 'Do I need to move furniture before the painting process?', 'We recommend clearing the furniture area to ensure a smooth and practical application. Our team can guide you on what needs to be moved, or we can help with this as part of the service.'),
(239, 83, 'How do I maintain my painted parquet floors?', 'To keep your floors looking beautiful, clean them with a soft broom or a damp mop. Avoid harsh chemicals or rough materials that may damage the finish. Regular care will ensure your floors stay stunning for years.'),
(240, 83, 'Do you offer a warranty for your parquet painting services?', 'Yes! We offer a satisfaction guarantee on all our services. If you’re unhappy with the results, we’ll work quickly to resolve any issues.'),
(241, 85, 'How long does the move-in or move-out painting service take?', 'The time needed depends on the size of your property and the amount of painting required. Typically, it takes between 1 and 3 days. We work efficiently to ensure minimal disruption to your schedule.'),
(242, 85, 'Can you help with choosing colours?', 'Yes! We offer colour consultation services to help you select the perfect shades for your space. Our team will guide you in finding colours that match your style and vision.'),
(243, 85, 'Do you offer eco-friendly paint options?', 'Definitely! We use low-VOC and odourless paints that are eco-friendly and safe for your health, ensuring a clean and fresh environment indoors. These paints not only reduce indoor air pollution but also contribute to a healthier living space for you and your family.'),
(244, 85, 'Is your painting service available on short notice?', 'We understand that moving can require quick turnarounds. Depending on availability, we can accommodate last-minute requests and complete the job on time.'),
(245, 85, 'Do I need to do any prep work before painting begins?', 'Our team handles all the preparation, including cleaning, sanding, and minor wall repairs. You don’t need to do anything—just leave the work to us!'),
(246, 85, 'Will the paint last, and is it durable?', 'Yes, we use high-quality, durable paints that provide a long-lasting finish, keeping your walls fresh and vibrant for years. Our paints are designed to withstand the test of time, ensuring that your investment in our services pays off in the long run.'),
(247, 85, 'How do I get a quote for your painting services?', 'Simply contact us to schedule a free consultation. We’ll assess the space and provide a precise, transparent quote based on your needs.'),
(248, 18, 'What is included in your office cleaning service?', 'Our office cleaning service is designed to cover all your cleaning needs. It includes thoroughly dusting and sanitising surfaces, vacuuming and mopping floors, restroom cleaning, waste management, and using eco-friendly practices. We can also tailor our service to meet your office\'s specific cleaning requirements.'),
(249, 18, 'How often should I schedule cleaning for my office?', 'The frequency of cleaning depends on your office size and needs. We offer daily, weekly, or monthly cleaning services. We can help you select the best schedule based on how often your office is used and your preferences.'),
(252, 18, 'Do you use eco-friendly cleaning products?', 'Yes, we are dedicated to sustainability. We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are safe for your employees and the environment.'),
(253, 18, 'Can I customise the cleaning schedule to fit my office\'s needs?', 'Absolutely! We understand that every office is unique. You can choose a cleaning schedule that best suits your needs, whether daily, weekly, or another arrangement.'),
(254, 18, 'How do I get a quote for your office cleaning services?', 'For a personalised quote, contact us with details about your office size, cleaning preferences, and any special requirements. We\'ll provide a clear, competitive pricing plan based on your needs.'),
(255, 18, 'Are your cleaners insured and trained?', 'Yes, all our cleaners are fully trained and insured, ensuring your office is in safe hands. We prioritise security and professionalism in every aspect of our service.'),
(256, 18, 'Can I request additional services beyond the standard cleaning package?', 'Certainly! We can accommodate your needs if you need extra services like carpet cleaning, window washing, or specialised tasks. Just let us know, and we\'ll create a custom service plan.'),
(257, 18, 'What areas do you serve in Dubai?', 'We offer office cleaning services throughout Dubai, serving businesses in various sectors. We are ready to assist whether you\'re in Downtown Dubai, Business Bay, or Jumeirah.'),
(258, 19, 'What does your residential cleaning service include?', 'Our residential cleaning services include dusting, vacuuming, mopping, and sanitising all areas of your home, including living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, and bathrooms. We also offer specialised services like carpet, window, and sofa cleaning.'),
(259, 19, 'How do I book a cleaning service?', 'Booking a service is easy! You can contact us by phone or fill out the booking form on our website. Once we have your details, we\'ll schedule a suitable cleaning time.'),
(260, 19, 'Do I need to provide cleaning supplies?', 'No, you don\'t need to worry about providing supplies. We bring all the eco-friendly cleaning products and equipment required for a thorough and safe clean.'),
(261, 19, 'How long does a cleaning service take?', 'The length of time varies depending on your home\'s size and the type of service you need. Typically, apartments and villas take a few hours, but we\'ll give you a more accurate time estimate when you book.'),
(262, 19, 'Can I customise my cleaning service?', 'Of course! We offer flexible cleaning packages to suit your needs. Whether you need a one-time deep clean or regular maintenance, we\'ll tailor the service to your requirements.'),
(263, 19, 'Are your cleaning products safe?', 'Yes, all our products are eco-friendly and non-toxic, making them safe for your family, pets, and the environment.'),
(264, 19, 'Do you offer same-day cleaning services?', 'We accommodate last-minute requests, but availability depends on our schedule. Please contact us directly to check if same-day service is possible.'),
(265, 19, 'How much does residential cleaning cost?', 'Our prices are competitive and vary based on your property size and the type of service required. Contact us for a personalised quote!\n'),
(266, 19, 'Is there a satisfaction guarantee?', 'Yes! We are committed to quality. We\'re here if you\'re not fully satisfied with our service. Your happiness is our top priority.'),
(267, 19, 'Do you clean on weekends or holidays?', 'We offer flexible scheduling and can clean on weekends and public holidays. Just let us know what works best for you!'),
(268, 103, 'What\'s the difference between regular cleaning and deep cleaning?', 'Regular cleaning involves surface-level tasks like dusting, vacuuming, and wiping down visible areas. On the other hand, deep cleaning goes further by targeting hidden dirt, grime, and allergens in hard-to-reach places, such as behind appliances, inside cupboards, and window tracks. It also includes sanitising high-touch areas like doorknobs and light switches.\n'),
(269, 103, 'How long does a deep cleaning service take?', 'he time needed for deep cleaning depends on your space\'s size and condition. Typically, home deep cleaning takes 3 to 6 hours, while larger spaces like villas or commercial properties may take longer. We will give you an estimated timeframe for when you will book.'),
(270, 103, 'Is the cleaning process safe for pets and children?', 'Our cleaning process is designed with your family\'s Safety in mind. We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products, ensuring a safe environment for your children, pets, and everyone in your home or office.\n'),
(271, 103, 'Do I need to be present during the deep cleaning?', 'You don\'t have to be home during the cleaning. However, we recommend an initial walkthrough to discuss any specific cleaning needs. You can leave us clear instructions, and we\'ll cover the rest!'),
(272, 103, 'How often should I schedule deep cleaning services?', 'We recommend deep cleaning every 3 to 6 months, depending on your space size and lifestyle. More frequent cleaning may be needed for commercial spaces or areas with high foot traffic to keep your environment pristine.'),
(273, 103, 'What areas do you cover in Dubai?', 'We proudly serve all areas of Dubai, including popular neighbourhoods like Downtown Dubai, Jumeirah, Dubai Marina, and beyond. No matter where you are, we\'re just a call away!'),
(274, 103, 'How do I book a deep cleaning service?', 'Booking is easy! You can call us directly or complete our online booking form. Our team will confirm the details and schedule your deep cleaning service at a time that suits you.'),
(275, 20, 'How often should I get my carpets professionally cleaned?', 'We recommend cleaning your carpets every 6 to 12 months, depending on foot traffic, pets, and household conditions. High-traffic areas may need more frequent cleaning to maintain cleanliness and extend the life of your carpet.'),
(276, 20, 'Are your carpet cleaning products safe for children and pets?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning solutions that are safe for children and pets. Our products clean effectively while keeping your loved ones\' health and safety in mind.'),
(277, 20, 'How long does the carpet cleaning process take?', 'The time required depends on the carpet size and condition, but typically, it takes 2 to 4 hours. We aim to provide fast, efficient service without compromising on quality.'),
(278, 20, 'Will my carpet be wet after cleaning?', 'Our advanced equipment is designed to minimise moisture, so your carpet should dry within 4 to 6 hours. We also avoid using too much water, which helps speed up the drying process.\n'),
(279, 20, 'Do you offer carpet cleaning services for commercial spaces?', 'Yes, we provide professional carpet cleaning services for residential and commercial properties in Dubai. Whether a small office or an ample commercial space, we have the experience and equipment to handle it.\n'),
(280, 20, 'Can professional carpet cleaning remove all types of stains?', 'While our advanced cleaning techniques can remove most stains, some may need unique treatments, especially those that have been set for a long time. Our team will assess the stains and suggest the best removal approach.'),
(281, 20, 'Do I need to move furniture before the cleaning?', 'It\'s helpful if you move larger furniture items to allow better access to the carpet. However, we can work around most furniture. If you need assistance, our team can help move lighter furniture during cleaning. Just let us know in advance if you need support.'),
(282, 20, 'Are the results of carpet cleaning permanent?', 'While our cleaning removes dirt, stains, and allergens, the results are not permanent. Regular maintenance is needed to keep your carpets looking fresh and to prevent the buildup of dirt and allergens.'),
(283, 21, 'How often should I schedule office carpet cleaning?', 'For offices with heavy foot traffic, we recommend cleaning every 3-6 months to maintain a clean and professional environment and extend the life of your carpets. For offices with less traffic, once a year may be enough.'),
(284, 21, 'Are the cleaning products you use safe for my employees?', 'Yes! At Neat & Healthy Cleaning, we use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are safe for your employees and the environment. Our solutions are effective yet gentle on everyone\'s health.\n'),
(285, 21, 'How long does the carpet dry after cleaning take?', 'Our advanced equipment ensures fast drying times. Most carpets dry within 4-6 hours, depending on thickness and room ventilation, allowing minimal disruption to your office routine.\n'),
(286, 21, 'Will shampooing remove tough stains from my carpet?', ' Yes! Our professional carpet shampooing service removes tough stains from coffee, ink, food, and more. We use specialised techniques and stain removers to make your carpets look as good as new.'),
(287, 21, 'Do you offer carpet cleaning services for large commercial spaces?', 'Absolutely! Whether you have a small office or an ample commercial space, we offer customised carpet cleaning solutions to meet your needs. Our team can handle offices of any size with care and efficiency.\n'),
(288, 21, 'How can I schedule a carpet cleaning service?', 'Booking your carpet cleaning is easy! Simply call us or click here to book online through our website, and we\'ll arrange a convenient time for your office cleaning.\n'),
(289, 22, 'How often should windows be cleaned in Dubai?', 'Because of dust and sandstorms, we recommend professional window cleaning every 2 to 3 months. This keeps your views clear and protects your windows from damage.'),
(290, 22, 'What is included in your window cleaning service?', 'Our window cleaning services include exterior and interior windows, frame and sill wipe-downs, stain removal, and streak-free polishing. We use eco-friendly products and professional tools.'),
(291, 22, 'Do you offer high-rise window cleaning services?', 'Yes! Our trained and certified team can safely clean windows on high-rise apartments, offices, and villas. We use special equipment and follow strict safety rules.'),
(292, 22, 'Are your cleaning products safe for children and pets?', 'Absolutely. We use non-toxic, eco-friendly cleaning solutions. They are safe for children, pets, and the environment, while providing excellent cleaning results.'),
(293, 22, 'How long does professional window cleaning take?', 'It depends on your property size and the number of windows. Most house window cleaning takes 1 to 3 hours, but bigger homes or high-rise buildings may take longer.'),
(294, 22, 'Can you remove hard water stains or salt deposits from windows?', 'Yes, we can. We are experts at removing hard water stains, mineral build-up, and salt deposits caused by humid and dusty weather.'),
(295, 22, 'Do I need to be home during the service?', 'Not always! If we can access the exterior, we can complete exterior window cleaning while you are away, providing a convenient and hassle-free service. We arrange a time that suits you for interior window cleaning, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind.'),
(296, 22, 'How much does window cleaning service cost in Dubai?', 'The cost depends on the size of your property and the condition of the windows. We offer transparent, competitive prices with no hidden charges, and free quotes for all our window cleaning services.'),
(300, 24, 'How often should I get my sofa professionally cleaned?', 'You should get your sofa professionally cleaned every 6 to 12 months. More frequent cleaning is better if you have pets, heavy use, or allergy sufferers at home. Regular sofa cleaning keeps your furniture fresh and helps it last longer.'),
(302, 24, 'Can steam cleaning damage my sofa?', 'No, steam cleaning couch methods are very safe when done by professionals. At Neat & Healthy Cleaning, we adjust the steam to suit your fabric type. This gives a deep clean without causing any damage or colour fading. Steam cleaning is one of the most effective methods for removing allergens and bacteria from your sofa, leaving it clean and safe for your family.'),
(303, 24, 'Do you clean both fabric and leather sofas?', 'Yes! We offer expert services for both. Our fabric sofa cleaner team works on textile upholstery, while our leather couch cleaner team uses soft, caring products to clean and protect leather furniture.'),
(304, 24, 'How long does it take for my sofa to dry after cleaning?', 'Usually, your sofa will dry in 4 to 6 hours after a professional sofa cleaning service. We use fast drying methods to ensure your furniture is safe and ready without fabric damage.'),
(305, 24, 'Will professional sofa cleaning remove all stains?', 'We remove most stains very well. Some very old or deep stains might not entirely disappear, but our treatments significantly reduce them while keeping your fabric safe.'),
(306, 24, ' Is your cleaning process safe for kids and pets?', 'Yes! We use eco-friendly and non-toxic products that are entirely safe for children, pets, and anyone with allergies. With Neat & Healthy Cleaning, your home stays healthy and clean, and your loved ones are always safe.'),
(307, 24, 'Do you offer home service for sofa cleaning in Dubai?', 'Yes, we do! Our team provides sofa cleaning services right at your home across Dubai. You don’t need to move anything — we bring everything needed to clean your sofas on-site.'),
(308, 23, 'How often should facade cleaning be done?', 'We suggest cleaning building facades once or twice a year in Dubai’s dusty and humid weather. Busy commercial buildings may need cleaning every three months to stay fresh and avoid damage.'),
(309, 23, 'Is facade cleaning safe for glass, stone, and metal surfaces?', 'Yes, absolutely. At Neat & Healthy Cleaning, we first check your building’s materials. We then use the safest methods, such as low-pressure washing for delicate areas, steam for stone, and eco-friendly treatments for metal and glass.'),
(310, 23, 'What cleaning methods are used for facade cleaning?', 'We pick the method that best suits your building. Our services include:\nPressure washing\n\n\nSteam cleaning\n\n\nRope access or manual cleaning\n\n\nEco-friendly chemical cleaning\n\n\nSoft washing for delicate surfaces\n'),
(311, 23, 'How long does a facade cleaning service take?', ' It depends on the size, height, and condition of your building. Most house facade cleaning jobs take 1–2 days. More significant commercial projects may need a few extra days. After checking your site, we give a full-time estimate.'),
(312, 23, 'Is facade cleaning environmentally friendly?', 'Yes. We use eco-friendly products that are biodegradable, non-toxic, and safe for people, pets, and plants, while still giving fantastic cleaning results.'),
(313, 23, 'Can you remove stubborn stains, mould, or hard water marks?', 'Of course! Our unique treatments remove stains, mould, mildew, and hard water marks.\n We bring back your building’s original look without harming the surface.'),
(314, 25, 'How often should I clean my AC?', 'Your AC should be cleaned every 6 to 12 months. If you live in a dusty place like Dubai or have allergies, cleaning it more often is best.\n'),
(315, 25, 'What’s included in your professional AC cleaning service?', 'Our service covers air duct cleaning, a/c vent cleaning, coil cleaning, drain line flushing, filter change, and full sanitising with eco-friendly products.\n'),
(316, 25, 'How do I know my AC needs cleaning?', 'Look for signs like musty smells, weak airflow, high power bills, dust around vents, or sneezing and coughing when the AC is on.'),
(317, 25, 'Can a dirty AC affect my health?', 'Yes. A dirty AC can blow out mould, dust, and bacteria, which can cause breathing issues, tiredness, and more, especially if you’re sensitive.\n'),
(318, 25, ' Do you clean both home and business AC systems?', 'We clean air conditioner systems in homes, offices, shops, and other commercial places across Dubai.'),
(319, 25, 'How long does it take to clean an AC?', ' For most homes, it takes 2 to 3 hours. More significant systems or business places may take longer—we’ll plan it to suit your needs.'),
(320, 25, 'Will my place get messy during the cleaning?', 'No, not at all. We keep everything tidy. Our team uses dust-control tools and leaves your space neat and fresh.'),
(321, 25, 'Can AC cleaning lower my electricity bill?', 'Yes. After AC cleaning, your system runs better and uses less energy, which helps cut down your monthly electricity costs.'),
(322, 29, 'How often should I clean my pool in Dubai?', 'Due to the heat and sand, weekly cleaning is recommended for residential pools. High-use or commercial pools may need 2–3 sessions per week.'),
(323, 29, 'Do you provide emergency pool cleaning?', 'Yes! We offer urgent same-day pool cleaning services in Dubai for sudden issues like green water, algae outbreaks, or party prep.'),
(324, 29, 'Are your chemicals safe?', 'Absolutely. We use eco-friendly, Dubai Municipality-approved chemicals that are safe for children, pets, and sensitive skin.'),
(325, 29, 'Can you also maintain pool equipment?', 'Yes. Our technicians clean and inspect filters, pumps, heaters, and valves. We notify you if repairs or replacements are needed.'),
(326, 29, 'How much does it cost?', 'Prices vary based on pool size and frequency. Starting from AED 150 per visit. Call us or WhatsApp for a free quote.'),
(327, 30, 'What’s the difference between power washing and pressure washing?', 'They’re similar, but power washing uses heated water, which is more effective for greasy, oily, or moldy surfaces.'),
(328, 30, 'Can power washing damage tiles or glass?', 'No, our trained team adjusts pressure based on the material. We ensure zero damage using commercial-grade nozzles and techniques.'),
(329, 30, 'How often should I power wash my property in Dubai?', 'We recommend every 3–6 months depending on exposure to dust, sand, and traffic.'),
(330, 30, 'Are your chemicals safe?', '100%. We use non-toxic, biodegradable products approved by Dubai authorities.'),
(331, 30, 'What’s the price of power wash cleaning?', 'Depending on surface area. Free estimate available upon site visit.'),
(332, 31, 'How often should I clean my water tank in Dubai?', 'Dubai Municipality recommends every 6 months. We also advise more frequent cleaning for commercial buildings or high-use villas.'),
(333, 31, 'Is the water safe to use right after cleaning?', 'Yes. Once cleaning and disinfection are complete, we flush and rinse the tank thoroughly. You can resume use within a few hours.'),
(334, 31, 'What chemicals do you use?', 'We use non-chlorinated, eco-friendly, Dubai-approved disinfectants that remove bacteria without leaving chemical residue.'),
(335, 31, 'Do I need to be home during the cleaning?', 'Not necessarily. If we have access to the tank and water supply, you can approve work remotely or via WhatsApp.'),
(336, 31, 'Do you provide certification for the cleaning?', 'Yes. We can provide a cleaning report or service certificate upon request, especially useful for commercial properties or rental units.'),
(337, 32, 'How often should a mattress be cleaned?', 'Every 6–12 months is ideal. For people with allergies or respiratory issues, we recommend every 3–6 months.'),
(338, 32, 'Can you remove urine or sweat stains?', 'Yes, we use enzyme-based stain removers and steam sanitization to treat body fluids, sweat, and mild urine stains effectively.'),
(339, 32, 'Is the process noisy or messy?', 'Not at all. Our machines are low-noise, compact, and mess-free. We leave your room cleaner than we found it.'),
(340, 32, 'How long does the cleaning take?', 'Most mattresses take 30 to 60 minutes to clean and 2–4 hours to fully dry.'),
(341, 32, 'Do you clean king, queen, and single mattresses?', 'Absolutely. We service all sizes and types, including memory foam, latex, hybrid, and orthopedic mattresses.'),
(342, 94, 'How often should my upholstery be cleaned?', 'We recommend professional upholstery cleaning every 6 to 12 months, depending on usage and exposure to dirt and allergens.'),
(343, 94, 'Extends the Life of Your Furniture', 'Dirt and grime act like sandpaper, gradually damaging the fabric and causing premature wear and tear. Regular professional cleaning protects the upholstery, keeping your furniture in top condition for years.'),
(344, 94, 'How long does the cleaning process take?', 'The duration depends on the furniture size and fabric type. Most jobs take 1 to 3 hours, with an additional drying time of 2 to 4 hours.'),
(345, 94, 'Can you remove tough stains from upholstery?', 'Yes, our specialized stain removal techniques can handle even the most stubborn stains, including wine, ink, and pet stains.'),
(346, 94, 'Do you offer same-day upholstery cleaning services?', 'Yes, we provide same-day cleaning services in Dubai, subject to availability.'),
(347, 33, 'How often should grout be professionally cleaned?', 'Most homes benefit from grout cleaning once or twice a year. High-traffic areas or commercial spaces may need more frequent service.'),
(348, 33, 'Can you remove all types of stains?', 'Our methods remove the majority of stains, including grease, mold, mildew, and discoloration. Some older stains embedded for many years may lighten but not disappear fully.'),
(349, 33, 'Is your cleaning process safe for natural stone tiles?', 'Yes, we adjust our techniques and products for every surface type, including natural stone, to avoid damage.'),
(350, 33, 'Do I need to be home during the cleaning?', 'Not necessarily. As long as we have access to the area, you can approve the work remotely and return to freshly cleaned floors.'),
(351, 33, 'How long does it take to dry?', 'Most areas are dry and ready for light use within a few hours.'),
(352, 34, 'How often should I clean my solar panels?', 'For Dubai’s dusty environment, most manufacturers recommend cleaning every 3–4 months. If you live near construction or in areas with heavy bird activity, monthly cleaning can be beneficial.'),
(353, 34, 'Will cleaning damage my panels?', 'No. We use purified water and non-abrasive brushes specifically designed for solar glass.'),
(354, 34, 'Can you clean panels installed on high rooftops?', 'Yes. Our technicians are fully trained and equipped with safety harnesses and extension tools to reach panels on any building.'),
(355, 34, 'How long does it take?', 'Most residential systems take 1–2 hours depending on size and access.'),
(356, 34, 'Do I need to be home during cleaning?', 'Not necessarily, as long as we have safe access to the panels.'),
(357, 93, 'Do you offer cleaning after working hours?', 'Yes. We specialize in cleaning during evenings, early mornings, weekends, or any time that suits your business.'),
(358, 93, 'Are your cleaning products safe for employees and customers?', 'Absolutely. We use only Dubai Municipality-approved, eco-friendly solutions safe for all environments.'),
(359, 93, 'Can you provide one-time deep cleaning?', 'Yes. We offer both one-off deep cleaning and ongoing maintenance plans.'),
(360, 93, 'Do you provide cleaning supplies and equipment?', 'Yes. Our team arrives fully equipped—so you don’t have to worry about anything.'),
(361, 26, 'How often should I clean my AC coils?', 'In Dubai, we recommend cleaning every 6–12 months due to constant dust and humidity.'),
(362, 26, 'Will coil cleaning damage my AC?', 'No. We use low-pressure washing and soft brushes designed for delicate coil surfaces.'),
(363, 26, 'Does coil cleaning include filter cleaning?', 'Yes. We can clean or replace filters as part of a comprehensive AC maintenance plan.'),
(364, 26, 'How long does it take?', 'Most services take 1–2 hours per unit, depending on size and condition.'),
(365, 27, 'How soon after Consultation should I schedule deep cleaning?', 'It’s best to schedule deep cleaning immediately after Consultation is completed to prevent dust and debris from settling into surfaces.'),
(366, 27, 'Is post-Consultation deep cleaning safe for my family and pets?', 'Yes, at Neat and Healthy Cleaning Services, we use eco-friendly cleaning products and advanced techniques to ensure a safe environment for your family and pets.'),
(367, 27, 'Can you remove paint splatters and adhesives from surfaces?', 'Absolutely! Our team is equipped to handle tough stains, including paint splatters and adhesives, without damaging surfaces.'),
(368, 27, 'How long does post-Consultation deep cleaning take?', 'The duration depends on the size of your space and the level of cleaning required. On average, it takes 4-8 hours for a standard home or office.'),
(369, 27, 'Do you offer customized cleaning packages?', 'Yes, at Neat and Healthy Cleaning Services, we offer tailored cleaning packages to meet your specific needs and budget.\n'),
(370, 27, 'What areas do you cover in dubai?', 'We provide post-Consultation deep cleaning services across all dubai areas.');
