(32, 2, 'MATTRESS CLEANING', 'Deep Mattress Cleaning for a Healthier, Fresher Sleep – Dust-Free, Germ-Free, Odor-Free', 'MATTRESS CLEANING-featured_image-1612991750932459.png', 'MATTRESS CLEANING-banner_image-2652761750932459.png', '', '<p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\"><strong>Sleep Healthier. Breathe Cleaner. Live Fresher.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">A clean bed doesn’t always mean a clean mattress. Hidden deep inside the layers are dust mites, dead skin cells, sweat stains, bacteria, and allergens — even if your mattress looks spotless on the surface.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">At </span><a href=\"https://neatandhealthycleaning.com/\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\"><strong>Neat &amp; Healthy Cleaning</strong></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">, we provide professional mattress cleaning services in Dubai that eliminate harmful particles and odors using eco-safe, deep-extraction technology. Whether it’s a home, hotel, or furnished apartment — we restore your mattress to a fresh, hygienic, and odor-free state so you can sleep in peace.</span></p><h3><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\"><strong>Why Choose Our Mattress Cleaning in Dubai?</strong></span></h3><h4><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">Deep Extraction Cleaning</span></h4><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">We use a multi-stage dry and steam extraction method that goes beyond the surface. Our process removes:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">Dust mites &amp; allergens</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">Sweat and urine stains</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">Bacteria, mold, and mildew</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\">Odors caused by body oils and humidity</span></li></ul><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:1080/1080;\" src=\"../../public/images/1750932155_-mattress-cleaning-neat and healthy